Update BIOS using Internet cable

(Set UEFI)
  Legacy Mode = Off (default)
  Secure Boot = Off
  Graphics = Discrete
  Port security = Off (for the dock)

Install Ubuntu 16.04 LTS

Trim launcher

Remove softwares

Update softwares & install additional drivers (Software Updater)

Add repositories
  $ sudo apt-add-repository ppa:git-core/ppa
  $ sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/atom

Install softwares
  $ sudo apt install screen tree gparted exfat-utils exfat-fuse atom git

Increase typing speed

Set File view (Edit --> Preferences)

Remove nautilus shortcuts
  $ vi ~/.config/user-dirs.dirs
  Use $HOME/Anamna/ instead of the media directories

Set vi as the default text editor
  $ sudo update-alternatives --config editor
